text.data-name: The Technical Working Groups (TWGs) will drive the plan's implementation. Tasked with planning and coordinating activities within specific collaboration areas, TWGs will monitor progress, maintain role clarity, and ensure accountability across tasks.

The Focal Points will be responsible for setting the vision and strategy. They act as the bridge between the partnership's activities and report to the leadership of the respective organizations involved.
